                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17990911-11-off55" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990911-11-off55" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990911-11-off55" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990911-11-cd56" type="crimeDate">5th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990911-11-off55 t17990911-11-cd56"></join>, six yards of cotton, value 10s. a cotton handkerchief, value 12d. a child's cap, value 12d. a child's nightgown, value 12d. and a child's petticoat, value 12d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17990911-11-victim115" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Lingham
                  <interp inst="t17990911-11-victim115" type="surname" value="Lingham"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990911-11-victim115" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
