                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990911-11-off55 t17990911-11-victim115"></join>
                  </persName>
               
            , the younger.(The prisoner, being a foreigner, he was tried by a Jury consisting of half Foreigners and half Englishmen.)</p>
         
